Support treatments can be useful for those people with mild symptoms and early stages of infection. WHO and the National Health Commission of China published recommendations for the care of people hospitalized with COVID-19.
Intensive and pneumologist physicians from the U.S.A. gathered recommendations for the treatment of several agencies in a free resource, the IBCC.
